  > MP_DS2SQUEEZE: work.smaller is    5MB

  @param [in] libds The library.dataset to be squeezed
  @param [out] outds= (work.mp_ds2squeeze) The squeezed dataset to create
  @param [in] mdebug= (0) Set to 1 to enable DEBUG messages

